 {
  "i": 31,
  "style": "Title",
  "name": "",
  "text": "{\\fad(2000,0)}Combination of Brains and Brawn!\\NOars and Moriah vs. the Straw Hats!"
 },
 {
  "i": 32,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "Brook... you can move again?"
 },
 {
  "i": 33,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "You saved me. Thanks a lot."
 },
 {
  "i": 34,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Brook",
  "text": "Certainly, I was seriously injured."
 },
 {
  "i": 35,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Brook",
  "text": "And as I bravely dragged my body to the kitchen in my quest for salt..."
 },
 {
  "i": 36,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Brook",
  "text": "I discovered a bottle of delicious milk and drank it, giving these results!"
 },
 {
  "i": 37,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "There's no way for calcium to be that effective!"
 },
 {
  "i": 38,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Brook",
  "text": "Milk can heal broken bones!"
 },
 {
  "i": 39,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Liar!"
 },
 {
  "i": 40,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Well, at any rate... we've obtained a large amount of salt at the very last minute."
 },
 {
  "i": 41,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "The way to the kitchen is blocked now."
 },
 {
  "i": 42,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "The salt that Brook has brought is our last hope."
 },
 {
  "i": 43,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "We're short on time."
 },
 {
  "i": 44,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "We have to fight!"
 },
 {
  "i": 45,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "If we make that monster swallow the salt,"
 },
 {
  "i": 46,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "And then beat Moriah immediately afterwards, we can win."
 },
 {
  "i": 47,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "You should be grateful that I came out to fight!"
 },
 {
  "i": 48,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "Also, I'd be extremely careful if I were you."
 },
 {
  "i": 49,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "I'm not here without a reason!"
 },
 {
  "i": 50,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "I'll make you experience your worst nightmare!"
 },
 {
  "i": 51,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Brook",
  "text": "Allow me to join your fight, as I promise to fight with all my might!"
 },
 {
  "i": 52,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Brook",
  "text": "I can't think of any other way to repay the great favor of recovering my shadow!"
 },
 {
  "i": 53,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Brook",
  "text": "I shall...!"
 },
 {
  "i": 54,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Brook",
  "text": "Creak..."
 },
 {
  "i": 55,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "Don't push yourself."
 },
 {
  "i": 56,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "Just hang on to that salt."
 },
 {
  "i": 57,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "I'll show you something special."
 },
 {
  "i": 58,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Franky",
  "text": "My anti-monster rounds."
 },
 {
  "i": 59,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Gotta take the initiative."
 },
 {
  "i": 60,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "The last one was too small for you."
 },
 {
  "i": 61,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Franky, I'm counting on you!"
 },
 {
  "i": 62,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Deadly Special Oil Star!"
 },
 {
  "i": 63,
  "style": "Main",
