  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Yes, we know you are."
 },
 {
  "i": 171,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "We're aware you have no time to lose."
 },
 {
  "i": 172,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Just give us a minute!"
 },
 {
  "i": 173,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "You're our only hope."
 },
 {
  "i": 174,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "We've been looking for you!"
 },
 {
  "i": 175,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "We're the Risky Brothers, henchmen of Lola the Proposer, Captain of the Rolling Pirates."
 },
 {
  "i": 176,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "You want to defeat Gekko Moriah, don't you?"
 },
 {
  "i": 177,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Don't you?"
 },
 {
  "i": 178,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "We know the secret to Moriah's ability."
 },
 {
  "i": 179,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "It'll grant you insurmountable power!"
 },
 {
  "i": 180,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "So please beat him for us."
 },
 {
  "i": 181,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Secret? Power?"
 },
 {
  "i": 182,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "What do you say?"
 },
 {
  "i": 183,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "That's why I'm asking you: what's on your mind?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 184,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Allow me to introduce her."
 },
 {
  "i": 185,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "The Captain of the Rolling Pirates, Lola the Proposer."
 },
 {
  "i": 186,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Her current total of proposals is 4,443."
 },
 {
  "i": 187,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "My! I like you."
 },
 {
  "i": 188,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "Marry me."
 },
 {
  "i": 189,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "No."
 },
 {
  "i": 190,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Both",
  "text": "He rejected her!"
 },
 {
  "i": 191,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Both",
  "text": "That's the 4,444th person who's rejected her!"
 },
 {
  "i": 192,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Anyway, we're part of the group of victims that have been stripped off their shadows..."
 },
 {
  "i": 193,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "And are doomed to wander the forest."
 },
 {
  "i": 194,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "I also had my shadow stolen, so I have no time to lose!"
 },
 {
  "i": 195,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "You're Straw Hat Luffy, aren't you?"
 },
 {
  "i": 196,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "In any case, there's never been so much chaos in Thriller Bark before!"
 },
 {
  "i": 197,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Moriah's three servants have been obliterated and there's barely anything left of his mansion."
 },
 {
  "i": 198,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Yeah, we all have been very excited since you came."
 },
 {
  "i": 199,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "But... rumor has it that the enemy's trump card, the Special Zombie, has been awakened!"
 },
 {
  "i": 200,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "We receive information via our Victim Network."
 },
 {
  "i": 201,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "We've been without shadow for three years now!"
 },
 {
  "i": 202,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "We don't wanna keep living like this!"
 },
 {
  "i": 203,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "If you manage to defeat Moriah, we can all have our shadows back!"
 },
 {
  "i": 204,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Then again, we're in trouble!"
 },
 {
  "i": 205,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Do you know Moriah's current location?"
 },
 {
  "i": 206,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Inside his belly!"
 },
 {
  "i": 207,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "He's inside that monster's belly!"
 },
 {
  "i": 208,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "What?! He was eaten?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 209,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "That's not it."
 },
 {
  "i": 210,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "He's riding in his belly."
 },
 {
  "i": 211,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Basically, unless you defeat the special zombie which has your shadow, you won't be able to reach Moriah."
 },
 {
  "i": 212,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "He's fighting your friends in the mansion's courtyard."
 },
 {
  "i": 213,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "What?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 214,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Damn it!"
 },
 {
  "i": 215,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Then I have no time to lose!"
 },
 {
  "i": 216,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "I told you to wait!"
 },
 {
  "i": 217,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "Save the sluggish explanations for later!"
 },
 {
  "i": 218,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "Showing him an example is faster!"
 },
 {
  "i": 219,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "An example of the shadows' secret we've discovered!"
 },
 {
  "i": 220,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Yes!"
 },
 {
  "i": 221,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Move it! Move it!"
 },
 {
  "i": 222,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Here it comes!"
 },
 {
  "i": 223,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "A shadow?"
 },
 {
  "i": 224,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Yes, a shadow!"
 },
 {
  "i": 225,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Shadows that are released upon feeding a zombie with salt can be grabbed with your bare hands!"
 },
 {
  "i": 226,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Here goes!"
 },
 {
  "i": 227,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "W-What's all this?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 228,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "You're stabbing me with a shadow!"
 },
 {
  "i": 229,
  "style": "Secondary",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Hang in there."
 },
 {
  "i": 230,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Stop!"
 },
 {
  "i": 231,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "I'm losing consciousness..."
 },
 {
  "i": 232,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Alright!"
 },
 {
  "i": 233,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "It's in!"
 },
 {
  "i": 234,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "Well?"
 },
 {
  "i": 235,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "Are you back to your senses?"
 },
 {
  "i": 236,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Yeah."
 },
 {
  "i": 237,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "Can you use a sword?"
 },
 {
  "i": 238,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Not... in the very least."
 },
 {
  "i": 239,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "W-What happened?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 240,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "The shadow which entered your body just now... is that of a skilled marine swordsman."
 },
 {
  "i": 241,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "All the power the shadow possesses is added to your own!"
 },
 {
  "i": 242,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Furthermore, you can keep adding shadows as long as you hold on to your senses!"
 },
 {
  "i": 243,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "Amazing, isn't it?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 244,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "We can take advantage of Moriah's ability to dramatically increase your strength!"
 },
 {
  "i": 245,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "We've caught plenty of shadows."
 },
 {
  "i": 246,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "However; if you don't have a strong mind and easily go unconscious, all the power will be wasted."
 },
 {
  "i": 247,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "How come you have that many shadows?"
 },
 {
  "i": 248,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "In order to find our shadows, we've been desperately purifying zombie after zombie."
 },
 {
  "i": 249,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "But we only found shadows of people we didn't know."
 },
 {
  "i": 250,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "So we started capturing them instead."
 },
 {
  "i": 251,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Listen, be sure to remember this."
 },
 {
  "i": 252,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "When a shadow is put into a corpse, that corpse becomes a zombie, but..."
 },
 {
  "i": 253,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "When it's put into a human with a soul and mind of its own, it can't settle down."
 },
 {
  "i": 254,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Your power-up will last 10 minutes, at best."
 },
 {
  "i": 255,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "After that, the shadow will go back to its original owner."
 },
 {
  "i": 256,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Do you understand?"
 },
 {
  "i": 257,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "It's a 10 minute match."
 },
 {
  "i": 258,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "All the shadows we've risked our lives to capture, will be given to you!"
 },
 {
  "i": 259,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "That many?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 260,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "The fog has already cleared. That means we only have 20 minutes of night left to strike."
 },
 {
  "i": 261,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "Anyway, we've gotta hurry."
 },
 {
  "i": 262,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "Hold on to your senses!"
 },
 {
  "i": 263,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "You should be able to handle 20 or 30 shadows!"
 },
 {
  "i": 264,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "Our limit is 2 or 3, at most."
 },
 {
  "i": 265,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "Go ahead!"
 },
 {
  "i": 266,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "W-Wait a minute!"
 },
 {
  "i": 267,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Isn't it too soon{\\fscx250}-{\\r}"
 },
 {
  "i": 268,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "T-This man...!"
 },
 {
  "i": 269,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "What kind of mind does he possess?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 270,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "I can't believe my eyes..."
 },
 {
  "i": 271,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "He absorbed 100 shadows straight!"
 },
 {
  "i": 272,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Unbelievable!"
 },
 {
  "i": 273,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "As expected from our ray of hope!"
 },
 {
  "i": 274,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "H-Hey!"
 },
 {
  "i": 275,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "How are you feeling?"
 },
 {
  "i": 276,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Are you still you?"
 },
 {
  "i": 277,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Straw Hat Luffy!"
 },
 {
  "i": 278,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Yeah."
 },
 {
  "i": 279,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "It's me."
 },
 {
  "i": 280,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "The power keeps... overflowing!"
 },
 {
  "i": 281,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "Somehow... you..."
 },
 {
  "i": 282,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "You've changed..."
 },
 {
  "i": 283,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirate",
  "text": "You were a bit smaller before."
 },
 {
  "i": 284,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "I'd never imagined this kid would be this strong."
 },
 {
  "i": 285,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "The thirst for battle..."
 },
 {
  "i": 286,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Is burning inside me!"
 },
 {
  "i": 287,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "You're ready to go!"
 },
 {
  "i": 288,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "Now, there's no time!"
 },
 {
  "i": 289,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "Show that accursed Moriah what nightmares are all about!"
 },
 {
  "i": 290,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "You're our last ray of hope!"
 },
 {
  "i": 291,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Lola",
  "text": "Nightmare Luffy!"
 },
 {
  "i": 292,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Just you wait!"
 },
 {
  "i": 293,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Luffy",
  "text": "Moriah!"
 },
 {
  "i": 294,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirates",
  "text": "Wait a minute!"
 },
 {
  "i": 295,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Pirates",
  "text": "You're going the wrong way!"
 },
 {
  "i": 296,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Oz",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,0)}Rubber..."
 },
 {
  "i": 297,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "Here he comes!"
 },
 {
  "i": 298,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Oz",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Bell!"
 },
 {
  "i": 299,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Oz",
  "text": "I feel better now that I can stretch."
 },
 {
  "i": 300,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Oz",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Spear!"
 },
 {
  "i": 301,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "Damn, what's going on?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 302,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "His attack power has greatly increased!"
 },
 {
  "i": 303,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "Why can Oars' body stretch without having a devil fruit's power?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 304,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "What did you do, Moriah?!"
 },
 {
  "i": 305,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "Yes! The real nightmare starts now!"
 },
 {
  "i": 306,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "Behold the Shadow power!"
 },
 {
  "i": 307,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Shadow Revolution!"
 },
 {
  "i": 308,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Brook",
  "text": "R-Revolution?"
 },
 {
  "i": 309,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "Shadows are bound to follow the body's orders."
 },
 {
  "i": 310,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "That's common sense."
 },
 {
  "i": 311,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "Body and shadow will always share the same form."
 },
 {
  "i": 312,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "That is an inviolable rule."
 },
 {
  "i": 313,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "However, right now..."
 },
 {
  "i": 314,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "Oars' shadow, which should be serving its body, is being manipulated by my own shadow."
 },
 {
  "i": 315,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "Can you tell what is happening?"
 },
 {
  "i": 316,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "I can change the shape of Oars' shadow at will."
 },
 {
  "i": 317,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "However, body and shadow must have the same shape."
 },
 {
  "i": 318,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "In order for body and shadow to be the same, the body is forced to obey the shadow and change with it."
 },
 {
  "i": 319,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "A shadow revolution!"
 },
 {
  "i": 320,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "In other words, by reversing common sense,"
 },
 {
  "i": 321,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Chopper",
  "text": "Moriah forced Oars' shadow to stretch, and thus the body was forced to stretch as well."
 },
 {
  "i": 322,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "So... it's not like Oars has turned into a rubber man..."
 },
 {
  "i": 323,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "He has become a monster that can turn into anything!"
 },
 {
  "i": 324,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Sanji",
  "text": "How convenient, for such a big monster!"
 },
 {
  "i": 325,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Zoro",
  "text": "Yeah, now it won't be easy to get near him."
 },
 {
  "i": 326,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "Soon you'll realize it's worse than rubber!"
 },
 {
  "i": 327,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "If I make his shadow round,"
 },
 {
  "i": 328,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "Oars will do the same!"
 },
 {
  "i": 329,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "{\\fad(150,150)}Oars Ball!"
 },
 {
  "i": 330,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "Take this!"
 },
 {
  "i": 331,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Usopp",
  "text": "Run away!"
 },
 {
  "i": 332,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Oz",
  "text": "Hey, hey! Wait a second, Master!"
 },
 {
  "i": 333,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Oz",
  "text": "Stop messing with my fight!"
 },
 {
  "i": 334,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "Sorry for that."
 },
 {
  "i": 335,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "I didn't mean to spoil your fun."
 },
 {
  "i": 336,
  "style": "Main",
  "name": "Moria",
  "text": "I'm here to give you a hand and nothing more."
